OL,3,C'We let people down,' says health
OL,4,Cminister after infected blood scandal
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland's Health Minister has
OL,8,Fsaid the findings of the infected
OL,9,Fblood scandal are a step in the right
OL,10,Fdirection for those affected but will
OL,11,Fnot bring solutions for all their
OL,12,Fchallenges.
OL,14,FRobin Swann said were a "long time
OL,15,Fcoming". He said the stories of those
OL,16,Faffected were "harrowing and humbling".
OL,18,FHe said he will look at the
OL,19,Frecommendations and see how they will
OL,20,Fapply to Northern Ireland.
