OL,7,FRishi Sunak told MPs: "Sir Brian finds
OL,8,Fa catalogue of systemic, collective
OL,9,Fand individual failures ` each on its
OL,10,Fown serious, and taken together
OL,11,Famounting to a calamity.J"And the
OL,12,Fresult of this inquiry should shake
OL,13,Four nation to its core. This should
OL,14,Fhave been avoided. It was known these
OL,15,Ftreatments were contaminated, warnings
OL,16,Fwere ignored repeatedly.J"Time and
OL,17,Fagain people in positions of power and
OL,18,Ftrust had the chance to stop the
OL,19,Ftransmission of those infections. Time
OL,20,Fand again they failed to do so."JThe
OL,21,Finfected blood scandal which claimed
OL,22,Fthousands of lives was "no accident",
OL,23,Fthe inquiry into the disaster
OL,24,Fconcluded.
