OL,3,C'We let people down,' says health
OL,4,Cminister after infected blood scandal
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FThere have been concerns from victims
OL,8,Fand campaigners for years there was a
OL,9,Fcover up by senior government and NHS
OL,10,Ffigures. The report compounds those
OL,11,Ffears by revealing key files "were
OL,12,Fdeliberately destroyed."
OL,14,F"Standing back, and viewing the
OL,15,Fresponse of the NHS and of government
OL,16,Foverall, the answer to the question
OL,17,F'was there a cover-up?' is that there
OL,18,Fhas been", Sir Brian said.
