OL,5,Creport
OL,7,F"Not in the sense of a handful of
OL,8,Fpeople plotting in an orchestrated
OL,9,Fconspiracy to mislead, but in a way
OL,10,Fthat was more subtle, more pervasive
OL,11,Fand more chilling in its implications.
OL,13,F"In this way there has been a hiding
OL,14,Fof much of the truth."
