OL,3,C'We let people down,' says health
OL,4,Cminister after infected blood scandal
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,F"Second to apologise for the repeated
OL,8,Ffailure of the state and our medical
OL,9,Fprofessionals to recognise the harm
OL,10,Fcaused. This includes the failure of
OL,11,Fprevious payment schemes, the
OL,12,Finadequate levels of funding made
OL,13,Favailable and the failure to recognise
OL,14,Fhepatitis B victims.
OL,16,F"And third, to apologise for the
OL,17,Finstitutional refusal to face up to
OL,18,Fthese failings and worse to deny and
OL,19,Feven attempt to cover them up."
